prompts.frontCover:
A vibrant and funny birthday card front cover, minimalist flat 2D vector art style. Against a clean, solid off-white background, Jordan and Lao Lao from the reference photo are transformed into cute, minimalist cartoon characters. Jordan is joyfully sitting in a classic snowboarder pose on a stylized, simple snowboard that is cleverly designed to look like a piece of Wagyu steak, complete with white marbling patterns. He is smiling widely, wearing the dark t-shirt from the photo. Lao Lao, wearing her white jacket, stands beside him with a happy, laughing expression, holding a pair of oversized chopsticks.

Floating playfully around them are various iconic items representing their shared interests: a minimalist salmon nigiri sushi piece, a cute smiling dumpling from a Chinese takeout box, and a simple laptop with binary code (0s and 1s) forming a heart shape on the screen. The entire composition is dynamic and full of movement, with clean lines, simple shapes, and a bright, cheerful color palette.

Centered in the middle of the design is the text "Happy Birthday, Jordan!" written in a beautiful, readable, elegant handwritten cursive script in a dark grey color.
